Type: Package
Package: gibasa
Title: An Alternate 'Rcpp' Interface to 'MeCab'
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Akiru", "Kato", , "paithiov909@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Akiru Kato <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: Gibasa is a plain 'Rcpp' interface to 'MeCab', a CJK
    tokenizer and morphological analysis tool. The main goal of gibasa
    package is to provide an alternative to 'tidytext' for CJK text data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://paithiov909.github.io/gibasa/
BugReports: https://github.com/paithiov909/gibasa/issues
